Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reset_clock_gating_check(25.10)                reset_clock_gating_check(25.10)

Name
       reset_clock_gating_check

Syntax
       reset_clock_gating_check

       [-setup]

       [-hold]

       [-rise]

       [-fall]

       [-high | -low]

       [<object_list>]

       Resets  the  specified setup and hold values for clock gating checks to
       the default values.

Parameters
       -high | -low
              Resets the non-controlling value (high or low) of the clock.

       -hold  Resets clock gating hold values.

       -rise | -fall
              Resets the specified setup (or hold) value  to  the  rising  (or
              falling) signals on the specified pins.

       -setup Resets clock gating setup values.

       <object_list>
              Specifies  a  list of clocks, instances, or pins for which clock
              gating checks are to be reset to default values.

              If the <object_list> parameter is not specified, the clock  gat-
              ing check is reset on the current design.

Related Information
              * set_clock_gating_check

